attributes.title: Last Laugh Season 2 Official Trailer
attributes.caption: Rooster Teeth’s hit show is back for another season! With new surprises, challenges, and rules, our twelve contestant’s composure is being put to the ultimate test. Season 2 premieres September 9 on Rooster Teeth!
attributes.description: Rooster Teeth’s hit show is back for another season! With new surprises, challenges, and rules, our twelve contestant’s composure is being put to the ultimate test. Who will break first? Find out when Season 2 premieres September 9 on Rooster Teeth!

attributes.title: They STILL Can’t Laugh - Episode 1
attributes.caption: A cast of new competitors and returning comedic pros are bringing their A-game into season 2, but will they be able to outlast their rivals and outsmart the host’s new evil games?
attributes.description: A cast of new competitors and returning comedic pros are bringing their A-game into season 2, but will they be able to outlast their rivals and outsmart the host’s new evil games? With three lives to spare and duffels full of derp, dignity and decorum are thrown out the window as contestants will do anything to make their opponents break. Keep watching to find out who will get this season’s last laugh!

attributes.title: The Long Island Last Laugh Talent Competition - Episode 2
attributes.caption: To refocus the game, the hosts put together a talent competition just crazy enough to make a few players crack. Gus and Kayla try not to get caught up in their own bit while Ryan goes full on psycho under the pressure.
attributes.description: To refocus the game, the hosts put together a talent competition just crazy enough to make a few players crack. Gus and Kayla try not to get caught up in their own bit while Ryan goes full on psycho under the pressure.
attributes.display_title: The Long Island Last Laugh Talent Competition - Episode 2

attributes.title: Strip Down and Nussy Up – Episode 3
attributes.caption: The first elimination hits the Laughers hard as Game Master James continues to up the ante by sending in some familiar faces and classic Rooster Teeth bits.
attributes.description: The first elimination hits the Laughers hard as Game Master James continues to up the ante by sending in some familiar faces and classic Rooster Teeth bits. And even though our competitors are on the spot, when James drops another bomb on the room, the threat of elimination becomes life or death.
attributes.display_title: Strip Down and Nussy Up – Episode 3

attributes.title: Robo-James Is Born - Episode 4
attributes.caption: Our players begin to drop like flies from the competition as a new wave of comedic cameos and challenges enter the Blue Room. Between sudden death, possible unemployment, and a bionic Gamemaster James, the Laughers do their best to keep their cool.
attributes.description: Our players begin to drop like flies from the competition as a new wave of comedic cameos and challenges enter the Blue Room. Between sudden death, possible unemployment, and a bionic Gamemaster James, the Laughers do their best to keep their cool.

attributes.title: Serial Killer Level Gags - Episode 5
attributes.caption: Seven competitors are still standing in the penultimate episode of the season, and just when we thought things couldn’t get any weirder, Robo-James pays the Laughers a visit and Blaine reveals a pretty hairy secret.
attributes.description: Seven competitors are still standing in the penultimate episode of the season, and just when we thought things couldn’t get any weirder, Robo-James pays the Laughers a visit and Blaine reveals a pretty hairy secret.

attributes.title: And the Last Laugh Goes to... - Episode 6
attributes.caption: We’re down to the finale and six competitors are still up against James’s bevy of surprises. With the thousand dollar prize close enough to taste, which player will remain stoic in the face of all that is comedy and have the Last Laugh?
